description: React component for uploading Excel files, handling user input, and making API calls to upload the selected file.

methods.name: ExcelUpload
methods.description: React component that provides an interface for uploading Excel files, manages state for file selection, error messages, and upload status, and handles the upload process.

methods.name: handleUpload
methods.description: Event handler function for form submission that uploads the selected Excel file to the server and triggers the onUpload callback with the server response.
